# Manual Download List

Place downloaded PDFs in `paper/references/` using the suggested filenames below.
Items are listed here because they have not yet been downloaded into the repository.

- [ ] `leland_taqqu_willinger_wilson_1994_ethernet_self_similar.pdf`
  - Leland, W. E., Taqqu, M. S., Willinger, W., & Wilson, D. V. (1994).
    "On the self-similar nature of Ethernet traffic."
    IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 2(1), 1-15.
  - DOI/search: `10.1109/90.282603`

- [ ] `pipiras_taqqu_2017_lrd_self_similarity.pdf`
  - Pipiras, V., & Taqqu, M. S. (2017).
    Long-Range Dependence and Self-Similarity.
    Cambridge University Press.
  - DOI/search: Cambridge University Press book page.

- [ ] `beran_1994_statistics_long_memory_processes.pdf`
  - Beran, J. (1994).
    Statistics for Long-Memory Processes.
    Chapman and Hall.
  - DOI/search: book title and author.

- [ ] `taqqu_teverovsky_willinger_1995_estimators_lrd.pdf`
