    "Estimators for long-range dependence: an empirical study."
    Fractals, 3(4), 785-798.
  - DOI/search: `10.1142/S0218348X95000692`

- [ ] `paxson_1997_fast_fgn.pdf`
  - Paxson, V. (1997).
